com.threecubed.auber.entities

Class GameEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.threecubed.auber.entities.GameEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Npc, Player, Projectile

    public abstract class GameEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    The GameEntity class is the abstract class from which all entities, including the player must inherit from. It contains information regarding the speed and max speed of entities, code to render an entity to the game world and for entities like the Player, information information regarding friction and velocity and collision handlers.
    Since:
    1.0
